                        <support> Text block comprised of sized and polished, medium-weight, heavily flocked, straw-coloured <material>paper</material>, both straight and cross-grain, possibly handmade in <country
                              cert="medium" ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7000208">India</country>.</support>
                        <extent>
                           <measure unit="folios" quantity="362">362 folios (ff. v + 362 + i)</measure>
